{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_12_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 葵と私の話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……前の仕事が押したから、次の現場への到着は\n少し遅れそうね……。あら、葵からメッセがきたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… the previous job ran long‚ so getting to the next location\nlooks like it’ll be a little delayed… Oh‚ a message from Aoi just came in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9811377343,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3552.195599,
          "startTime": 9.5333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 5.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5666655858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "愛とこころも到着したそうよ\n「コメント録りは先に始めててちょうだい」――っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai and Kokoro have arrived too‚ apparently.\n“Go ahead and start recording the comments first‚” she says.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3030.3344965,
          "startTime": 14.5970000823
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6700.001080900001,
          "startTime": 18.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日はついに……あの番組の撮影ですね\n莉央さん、緊張してますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s finally the shoot for that program…\nRio-san‚ are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1423345566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "別に、そんなに身構えてはいないわよ\nむしろ、こんな番組観てくれる人いるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really. I’m not that on edge about it.\nIf anything‚ I wonder if anyone will even watch a show like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8423356374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。BIG4になって\nファンがますます増えたおかげで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course they will. Since becoming one of the BIG4‚\nyour fanbase has grown even more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2436269443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "新しいファンから「過去のリズノワを知りたい」って\n要望が沢山届いたんでしょ。何度も聞いたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve received lots of requests from new fans saying\nthey want to learn about LizNoir’s past. I’ve heard it many times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8769613584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.9769587517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私達の仕事は、ファンの声に応えることだし\nドキュメンタリーを撮るのは構わない。でも名前が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our job is to listen to our fans‚\nso I don’t mind filming a documentary. But the title…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3436264992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺が考えた『LizNoir・BIG4までの軌跡\n～アイドルを夢見たっていいじゃない～』ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The title I came up with—“LizNoir: The Path to the BIG4\n~It’s Okay to Dream of Being an Idol~‚” you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3691582044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしいわよ、そのタイトル……貴方って\n仕事は出来るのに、こういうセンスは全然ないのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That title is embarrassing… honestly‚\nyou’re good at your job‚ but you have absolutely no sense for this kind of thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9358274778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "せめてその恥ずかしいサブタイトルだけは\n外してちょうだい。いいわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the very least‚ take off\nthat embarrassing subtitle. Understood?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4691608112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1024900119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いいタイトルだと思ったんですが……分かりました\nカットします。あ、そろそろロケ現場に到着しますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was a good title… but alright.\nI’ll cut it. Ah‚ we’re about to arrive at the location.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4434946067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 87.4268479348
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 87.4268479348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "……バンプロのオフィス、か\nまさか、こんな形で古巣に来ることになるとはね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Van pro’s office‚ huh.\nI never thought I’d come back to my old place like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7601822854,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 88.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりのバンプロですね。どうですか？\nやっぱり、懐かしいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a while since you were at Van Pro. How does it feel?\nDoes it feel nostalgic?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 102.5748036703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね。私が最初に入った事務所であり\nリズノワが生まれた場所だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. It’s the first agency I ever joined‚\nand the place where LizNoir was born.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5414744696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "そして、あの人……葵と私を会わせてくれた\n私をアイドルにしてくれた人と出会った場所でもあるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s also where I met the person who brought\nAoi and me together… the one who made me an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.374807803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 120.4748036703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "今ここにはいないけど……\nあの人なしに、私達は生まれなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He’s not here now‚ but…\nwithout him‚ we wouldn’t exist.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.074807803,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5100.0031154,
          "startTime": 125.5748067857
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ははははっ、そこまで言われると照れ臭いだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha! Hearing you say that makes me embarrassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6748036703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……久しぶりだな、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Long time no see‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.0748067857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 135.3748036703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さん！？　……ちょっと{user}さん\n三枝さんが来るなんて、聞いてないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saegusa-san!? …Hey‚ {user}-san.\nYou never told me Saegusa-san would be coming.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3414734524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 142.241470337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だって三枝さんは、リズノワを生み出した人で\nリズノワを語るなら、不可欠な存在でしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Saegusa-san is the one who created LizNoir‚\nso if we’re talking about LizNoir‚ he’s indispensable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9883127436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "リズノワがデビューしてすぐ、バンプロを辞めた俺には",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s too much praise for someone who left Van pro",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.1536923727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "過ぎた言葉だな。全ては彼女達自身の成果だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "right after LizNoir debuted. Everything is the result of their own efforts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.0870288214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 159.5870257061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんが私達を置いて行ったのは納得出来ないけど\n私と葵を引き合わせてくれたことは感謝してますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I still can’t accept that you left us behind‚\nbut I’m grateful that you brought Aoi and me together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0203621548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 168.0870307923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、こんな所でピリピリしても仕方がないわね\nでも、どうして三枝さんが来ることを黙っていたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ there’s no point getting tense here.\nBut why did you keep quiet about Saegusa-san coming?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.8536954881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すみません。当日まで三枝さんの仕事の都合がつくか\n分からなかったので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry. Until today‚ I wasn’t sure\nif his schedule would work out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大切な仕事だからな、都合もつけるさ。それより",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s important work‚ so I made the time. More importantly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.2019511224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 183.2019511224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さっき愛に聞いたんだが、葵がいなくなったらしいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Ai earlier that Aoi has disappeared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.6352824849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうやら機材トラブルで撮影が止まったらしくてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ the filming stopped due to equipment trouble‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.3019511224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "休憩の合間に踊りに行くと言って出て行ったそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and during the break she said she’d go dance and left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.5686158182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 203.2019511224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　すぐに機材が復旧したら、どうするのよ\nスタッフさん達を待たせちゃうじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? What if the equipment gets fixed right away?\nThe staff will be left waiting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.9019491515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、葵らしいですけどね。俺、探してきますよ\n三枝さん、少しの間現場をよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ that does sound like Aoi. I’ll go look for her.\nSaegusa-san‚ please keep an eye on things here for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.0831795905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 218.8097286543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "近くの公園を探してみるといいわ。バンプロにいた頃は\nよくあそこに逃走して一人で踊っていたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Try checking the nearby park. Back when we were at Van pro‚\nshe used to run off there and dance by herself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.3430600168,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7256.938012400014,
          "startTime": 226.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 226.9430670739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……まったく、デビューしてもう結構経つのに……\n葵の自由なところは変わらないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah… it’s been quite a while since our debut…\nbut Aoi’s free-spirited nature hasn’t changed at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.1763984364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 236.3597337406
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 236.3597337406
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さんの助言のおかげで、葵の捕獲に成功した俺は）\n（莉央さんのコメント録りになんとか間に合った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thanks to Rio-san’s advice‚ I managed to track Aoi down‚）\n（and somehow made it back in time for Rio-san’s comment recording.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、一旦、ここで休憩に入ります\n莉央さん、お疲れ様です。飲み物をどうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ we’ll take a break here for now.\nRio-san‚ good work. Here’s a drink.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 251.4328172048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。別に疲れてはいないわよ\n葵を探して走り回ってた貴方に比べたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. I’m not really tired.\nEspecially compared to you‚ running around looking for Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.1661434811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "でも……疲れはしないけど、昔話をするのは\n少し恥ずかしいわね。貴方と初めて会った時のこととか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… even if I’m not tired‚ talking about the past\nis a little embarrassing. Like when I first met you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.4994829179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 268.6328233083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は衝撃でした。「もうすぐいなくなる人の名刺を\n持っている意味はないでしょ？」って言われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That moment really shocked me. You said‚ “What’s the point of holding on\nto the business card of someone who won’t be around much longer?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 276.1997618358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなこともあったわね。あの時は私\n少しピリピリしてたから……悪いと思ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right‚ that did happen. Back then‚ I was\na little on edge… I do feel bad about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.733088112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。そりゃ少し驚きましたけど、あの頃の莉央さんが\nいろんなものを抱え込んでたって、今は知ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I was surprised‚ sure‚ but now I know\nyou were carrying a lot back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 293.8498297374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。私達がデビューしてすぐ、信頼していた\n三枝さんがバンプロを辞めてしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Right after we debuted‚\nSaegusa-san‚ whom we trusted‚ left Van pro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.1831560136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、私が心から信じられる存在は、お母さんと\n……葵だけだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since then‚ the only people I could truly trust were my mother and…\n…Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.6831560136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 310.6498195649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "それ以外の人達には、デビュー以来ずっと\n壁を作っていたから。貴方に対してもそうだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since our debut‚ I kept a wall between\nmyself and everyone else. That included you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.7831560136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 318.5164862316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい。雰囲気を暗くしちゃって\n気分を変えて、とっておきの話をさせてもらえる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry. I made the mood gloomy.\nLet’s change the mood. May I tell you a special story?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.0498226803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 325.6498195649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_01-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "貴方がまだ知らない、葵と私の話\nあれは、私達が初のワンマンライブを控えた頃――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A story about Aoi and me that you still don’t know.\nIt was around the time we were preparing for our very first solo live—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.9498226803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
